lead_paragraph: Bill Rancic embraces the notion of being part of a power couple with wife Giuliana. Both together and separately they have pretty busy careers, made exponentially more intense with the arrival of their son, Edward Duke, last year.

headline.main: Rancic on Being a Power Couple With E! News Wife
